import Documentation from './assets/celestiaDocumentation.svg'
import Blobspace from './assets/blobspace.svg'
import Blob from './assets/blob.svg'

const Resources = [
    {
        title: "Celestia Documentation",
        sub: "Documentation for the Celestia network.",
        button: "Explore",
        image: Documentation
    },
    {
        title: "Pay for blobspace",
        sub: "Overview of paying for blob transactions and Celestia’s fee market.",
        button: "Learn",
        image: Blobspace
    },
    {
        title: "Blob tutorial",
        sub: "Learn how to publish and retrieve transaction data from Celestia.",
        button: "Follow",
        image: Blob
    }
]

export default Resources
